title: PMS 2.0 323 - Happy New Years Eve With Mark Madden, Sam Roberts, Corey Graves, Ariel Helwani, & AJ Hawk
description: On today's show, Pat and the boys look back at their favorite moments from 2020, look ahead to 2021, and are joined by several special guests to ring in the New Year and put 2020 in our rear view.  Be safe tonight and this weekend, we'll see you on Monday. Cheers. Happy New Year.
dc:creator: Pat McAfee
